cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "TraitTrawler"
abstract: >-
  An autonomous AI agent that searches, retrieves, triages, and extracts
  structured phenotypic trait data from the scientific literature. Runs
  inside Claude Cowork and can be adapted for any taxon and trait by
  editing three configuration files.
